        "timestamp": "2018-08-31 16:37:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nI wonder will the API component have an independent life as a separate component or simply be a Java library that other components will use. If not, then it may not need start stop, command line arguments, and activation.\n\nAlso on parameters, it probably won't need a separate parameter handler as that type of functionality will be in the executable component that calls the library.",
