        "timestamp": "2018-08-31 19:45:50.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nLiam, my opinion was there would be REST entry point for the API. Which is what we have today. Of course the majority of the code would be in a sub-module and ultimately a jar file. We can discuss more.",
